snippet.textOriginal:
There was a bot and a pro who lived in an arena where only one can remain
They both had to settle their differences 
They fought through days and nights
After Bot could not hold in any longer he decided to drink a potion
Not an ordinary one 
One that heeled him
He had to find a safe place to camp in
The Bush
Pro in the other hand knew that another shot would eliminate Bot
As Bot saw Pro sweatily peaking and whipping 90s he waited for the perfect time for a headshot snipe
The time had come
Pro stood still as he needed to go to the toilet
Bot took the shot 
BUT...
The bullet flew through his hair
Pro came back from the toilet and wanted to end it
BUT...
Bot pickaxed him...:/

RIP Pro

For the 0.136% of people reading this hope you have a nice day..If you want to make mine I would really appreciate it if you could subscribe to my channel;)Even if you don’t..MAY THE FORCE BE WITH YOU
